ygData.messageBody:
U got it. the quest is not very well known of..and they are indeed ogres.
kill them both and take there heads to the same guy that u get the
bloodforge hammer from. give them both at the same time and you will get the
Blackened iron crown which is the exact same one as found in runnyeye found
on the goblin WARLORD...(not the king as most think....).the king drops it
but it is VERY VERY VERY rare for him to drop the crown.. the warlord is
easier to kill and he drops it often.
